<h3 id="launchpad-campaigns">Launchpad Campaign Scheduling</h3>

Launchpad lets you schedule and automate product launches, sales events, and theme changes in advance. For luxury brands running seasonal campaigns across multiple time zones, this eliminates 3 AM manual deployments and human error risk.

We use Launchpad for every limited-edition drop we manage. You can stage the entire experience—updated homepage, activated products, adjusted prices, marketing pixels—and execute with a single scheduled trigger. Post-campaign, everything reverts automatically.

<h3 id="scripts-editor">Script Editor for Custom Logic</h3>

The Script Editor enables custom Ruby scripts for line-item, shipping, and payment modifications at checkout. Luxury applications include tiered discounting for VIP customers, automatic gift-with-purchase logic, and sophisticated shipping rules based on product combinations or customer segments.

<div class="callout-blue">
<strong>Tip:</strong> Script Editor is being deprecated in favor of Shopify Functions. New implementations should use Functions exclusively. Existing scripts continue working, but plan migration before end-of-2027.
</div>

